node.title: Man in custody after sudden death at Mackay caravan park
node.alt: Three police officers walking on a grassy field.

node.content:
["A man is in custody after a 25-year-old mad died suddenly near a\u00a0North Queensland caravan park this morning.", "Emergency services were called to The Park Mackay in Paget\u00a0about 3am to reports of the sudden death.", "\"Another man has been taken into custody and is assisting police with their inquiries,\" a Queensland Police spokesperson said.\u00a0", "\"Investigations are ongoing and there is no further information at this time.\"", "No charges have been laid.\u00a0", "", "
A crime scene has been set up at The Park Mackay after reports of the sudden death.\u00a0(ABC Tropical North: Melissa Maddison)
", "Crime scenes have been established at the caravan park and an empty block of land near it.\u00a0", "The caravan park is located on Broadsound Road, which is also a part of the Bruce Highway.\u00a0", "Police are expected to address the media over the incident later this morning.\u00a0"]
